## About TRAVEL+ Budapest

TRAVEL+ is Hungary's international tourism fair and adventure festival, combining traditional travel exhibition with outdoor adventure experiences. Running concurrently with the Budapest Boat Show and Caravan Salon, this event attracts travel enthusiasts and industry professionals.

## Event Focus

Destinations | Hotels & Resorts | Adventure Travel | Outdoor Activities | Cultural Tourism | Travel Services

## Highlights

**200+ Exhibitors** and **30,000+ Visitors** make TRAVEL+ Hungary's premier tourism event, offering comprehensive travel inspiration and business opportunities.

## Why Attend

Discover new destinations, plan travel adventures, connect with tourism professionals, and access the Central European travel market.
